üé¨ Automated Workflow: Clipchamp ‚Üí GitHub ‚Üí YouTube

This README outlines a fully automated pipeline for exporting videos from Clipchamp, uploading them to GitHub for version control and distribution, and publishing them to YouTube with metadata and discoverability enhancements.

‚úÖ Quick Checklist for Uploading Your Clipchamp Video to YouTube

Export your video from Clipchamp as Unapologetically_Trailer.mp4.

Upload the video file to your GitHub repo under /assets/videos/.

Commit and push your changes to GitHub.

The GitHub Action workflow will automatically upload the video to YouTube using your stored API credentials.

After upload, embed the YouTube video link or player in your README using the provided markdown or HTML snippets.

‚öôÔ∏è Workflow Overview

Export from Clipchamp

Upload to GitHub

Trigger GitHub Action

Auto-publish to YouTube

Embed YouTube link in README

